window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>I’d never hidden the type of guy I was to anyone.</p> <p>Geeky, nerdy and unashamed of the presence I brought to a room.</p> <p>It was meant to be only one night.</p> <p>Hot, steamy and passionate…</p> <p>Where the geek actually got the unattainable god.</p> <p>Except he changed the rules and decided that he wanted more.</p> <p>I never expected when I jumped at the opportunity of my dream career that he’d be there.</p> <p>It was as if the stars had aligned up in the sky and were giving me a sign.</p> <p>But am I truly enough for this…for him even?</p>"; 
